{
  "id": "s1_cena_famiglia",
  "audio_theme": "ritorno_casa",
  "stat_entry": [
    {
      "stat": "legame",
      "op": "gte",
      "value": 70,
      "goto_branch": "intro_calda",
      "prepend": true
    }
  ],
  "pages": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p0_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Evening. The kitchen smells of butter and eggs. Mallow is at the stove with the air of someone about to reveal a family secret."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Two eggs. You crack them like this, put cheese inside, fold them like a calzone. You fry them. It's called 'calzuovo.' My grandmother's recipe."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex stares at him from the high chair. Not at the calzuovo. At him. With detective eyes."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "Calzuovo. I like it. Sounds like something you eat and then go into battle."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t5",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Exactly. It's the warriors' dish. Or at least hungry programmers'."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p1_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "The calzuovo arrives at the table. Mallow serves it with the pride of a Michelin-starred chef. Lex looks at the plate. Then at Favilla. Then at the plate again."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t2",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "He's plotting. I can tell. He has the same face as in the pasta aisle."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex pushes the plate away. He doesn't eat. He squints. Points his little finger toward Favilla. Then toward Mallow. Back and forth."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "What's up with you tonight? You don't like calzuovo?"
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t5",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "It's not the calzuovo. It's his mother. He's trying to tell you."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p2_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex is now staging a small sabotage. The spoon falls. Then the cup. Then the bib. One object at a time, with increasing emphasis on the target: Favilla."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Mallow looks at him. Then at Favilla. Then back at Lex. Something clicks."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t3",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "You know what's weird? For a few weeks now, every time something... strange happens, he does exactly this."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t4",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "He knows. He doesn't know. But he feels it. And Lex is serving it to him on a silver platter."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p3_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p3_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Mallow puts down his fork. Dinner is halfway through. Lex has stopped throwing objects and is staring at Favilla with unprecedented intensity."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p3_a_t2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Favilla. There's something you're not telling me."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p3_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He's not angry. He's... gentle. As if he's asking permission to know."
            }
          ],
          "choice": {
            "id": "cena_choice",
            "prompt": "Mallow looks at you. Lex too. Dinner is a powder keg.",
            "options": [
              {
                "id": "confessa_piccolo",
                "label": "\"Mallow... I need to tell you something. That Sunday at the park...\"",
                "goto_branch": "branch_confessa",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "legame": 8,
                  "segreto": -10
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "confessa_piccolo"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "facciata",
                "label": "\"Lex, eat. Mallow, this is delicious. Everything's fine.\"",
                "goto_branch": "branch_facciata",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "segreto": 8,
                  "resistenza": 5
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "facciata"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "umorismo",
                "label": "\"Mallow, your son is trying to direct a movie. Or maybe an exposé.\"",
                "goto_branch": "branch_umorismo",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "legame": 5,
                  "scintille": 5
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "umorismo"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "distrai_lex",
                "label": "You look at Lex. He has crayons in hand. He's drawing something.",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "segreto": -3
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "distrai_lex"
                },
                "minigame": {
                  "type": "disegna",
                  "tiers": [
                    {
                      "min": 4,
                      "label": "Disegno innocuo.",
                      "goto_branch": "branch_disegno_innocuo",
                      "stat_effects": {
                        "legame": 8,
                        "scintille": 5
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "min": 2,
                      "label": "Quasi...",
                      "goto_branch": "branch_disegno_quasi",
                      "stat_effects": {
                        "segreto": -5,
                        "legame": 3
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "min": 0,
                      "label": "Mallow ha visto.",
                      "goto_branch": "branch_disegno_visto",
                      "stat_effects": {
                        "segreto": -12,
                        "legame": 5
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "branches": {
    "intro_calda": {
      "id": "intro_calda",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "intro_calda_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow spent the afternoon at the stove. Calzuovo isn't just a recipe — it's a declaration. When Mallow cooks, he's saying what he can't put into words."
                },
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla knows. And it's exactly this warmth she risks losing if one day he finds out everything at the wrong time, in the wrong way."
                },
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "I thought that after the week you've had... you deserved a real dinner."
                },
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t4",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex from the high chair watches the scene. He's calculating. Tonight, dad is on his side."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "icalda_p0"
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_confessa": {
      "id": "branch_confessa",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_confessa_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla puts down her fork. Lex stops breathing — or so it seems, for a seven-and-a-half-month-old."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "That Sunday at the park... something happened. I don't know how to explain it. Even to myself."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow says nothing. He takes her hand. He waits."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Whenever you're ready, I'm here. I'm not going anywhere."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t5",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Not the whole truth. But a piece of it. Enough for tonight."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bconfe_p0"
        },
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_confessa_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex releases his breath. Then smiles — that conspiratorial two-tooth smile that says 'finally'."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "The calzuovo is almost cold. But Mallow's hand is still there, on top of hers."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_b_t3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Let's eat, before it gets cold. Then you can tell me the rest."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bconfe_p1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_facciata": {
      "id": "branch_facciata",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_facciata_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla smiles. A well-practiced smile. She changes the subject with the fluidity of someone who's done it many times before."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Everything's fine, really. Just tired. Corvi, the inspection. Heavy week. But this calzuovo is a miracle."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow nods. But he hasn't stopped looking at her. Lex snorts — frustrated, theatrical."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "I lied to him again. And Lex knows. And he's angry at me."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bfacci_p0"
        },
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_facciata_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow goes back to eating. Talks about work, about a new JavaScript library. The evening derails into normalcy."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "But Lex won't look at her anymore. He has his arms crossed on the high chair. Seven months old and already capable of holding a grudge."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_b_t3",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "I kept the secret. But I lost something with my son. I'll make it up tomorrow. Or maybe I won't."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bfacci_p1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_umorismo": {
      "id": "branch_umorismo",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_umorismo_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla looks at Lex. Then at Mallow. Then bursts out laughing — that real, full laugh she's almost forgotten she had."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Mallow, look at him. He has the face of someone trying to make us divorce. He's our tiny villain."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex makes a face — a kind of raspberry that sounds like 'I'm not a secret agent but I'm working on it'."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "He has more charisma than me. I say it with pride and a little fear."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bumori_p0"
        },
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_umorismo_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "All three of them laugh at the same moment. The calzuovo is finished, but it doesn't matter. For an instant, it's just a family having dinner."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex falls asleep shortly after, his head drooping. But he's smiling. He won something, even if he doesn't know what yet."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_b_t3",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Tomorrow everything will be complicated again. But not tonight. Tonight is ours."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bumori_p1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_disegno_innocuo": {
      "id": "branch_disegno_innocuo",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_innocuo_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex looks at his own drawing. The mom with fire hair now has normal hair. The sparks have become... little stars. Generic. Harmless."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "His masterpiece has been modified. By someone who had a gray crayon and suspicious knowledge of his plan."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex stares at Favilla with the expression of someone who just lost a chess match against their own mother."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "What a nice drawing! Is that us? Look, that's you, those are me and mom."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bdiseg_p0"
        },
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_innocuo_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Yes. The three of us."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow smiles. Lex crosses his arms on the high chair. Defeated. For now."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "The calzuovo is almost finished. The drawing is harmless. And Lex has learned that mom is faster than him even at the dinner table."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Nice try, little one. But I win tonight."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bdiseg_p1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_disegno_quasi": {
      "id": "branch_disegno_quasi",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_quasi_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla quickly modifies what she can. The result is a strange drawing: a figure with half-yellow, half-gray hair. A smile erased and redrawn."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "A crayon rolls away. Lex follows it with his eyes. Favilla picks it up before he can point at it."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "What's that? Let me see."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "A self-portrait by Lex. Abstract. He's talented."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bdiseg_p0"
        },
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_quasi_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex glares at her. Mallow laughs:"
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "He's talented."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "But he hesitated a second too long before laughing. That second in which he looked at the drawing more carefully than necessary."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "He didn't understand. But he felt there's something to understand. Tomorrow he'll think about it again."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bdiseg_p1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_disegno_visto": {
      "id": "branch_disegno_visto",
      "pages": [
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_visto_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow approaches while Favilla still has the crayon in hand. It's too late."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Who's that?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "He points to the fire hair. Favilla takes the sheet. Crumples it."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Nothing. Kid stuff."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bdiseg_p0"
        },
        {
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_visto_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "But Mallow doesn't look away. Lex smiles — he won."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "They look like... glowing hair. Like in the video."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "The silence lasts a second. Lex looks at Mallow. Mallow looks at Favilla. Favilla looks at the crumpled drawing."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "He connected the drawing to the video. My son just screwed me. With a crayon."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "id": "bdiseg_p1"
        }
